  &lt;p id="iZ4p4h"&gt;Once again, Amazon is holding a second Prime Day under the guise of &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/17/24244180/amazon-october-prime-day-big-deal-days-fall-dates-2024"&gt;Prime Big Deal Days&lt;/a&gt;, which runs through tomorrow, October 9th. While the naming convention might be terrible, the sale isn’t. In fact, many of our favorite gadgets and goods are receiving notable discounts right now, which we’ve highlighted in our larger roundup of the&lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024"&gt; best Prime Day deals&lt;/a&gt;. However, if you’re looking to stick to a budget, here’s where you’ll find our top picks under $50. &lt;/p&gt;
